repl_description:
KemisDigital is a comprehensive digital marketing and software development platform designed to provide technological solutions for Startups, NGOs, and Tourism sectors. The platform delivers a sophisticated web application with advanced features and robust technological integrations.

Tech Stack:
• React with TypeScript
• Shadcn UI Components
• OpenAI API Integration
• EmailJS for Contact Form
• Jitsi Meet Integration
• Responsive web design
• Modular component architecture
• Comprehensive portfolio management system
• Multi-section navigation system
